title: Patcher Stuck - Done everything to try and fix it. Still nothing. Rito pls help.
body:
I'm getting this issue where I get too 33% of my patch and it just errors out.. I've done everything I can to try and fix it, from repairing to reinstalling. I've sent logs aswell, if needed I can post here. But I've done literally everything I can to try and fix it, and no luck. Any thoughts?

http://puu.sh/fiQUd/22602bf965.jpg

replies.body: Reinstalling did not fix it for you? Do you have any programs installed on your machine which edits data lively?
Not that I know of, I'm using a dongle for an internet connection... That could be it?

Nope.

Reinstall League again, but be sure to delete the "Riot Games" folder from your PC before installing League again. The uninstaller does **not** remove it.
